OL,3,C'I caught Covid in 2020 and still live
OL,4,Cwith the effects five years later'
OL,6,FA man who says he is still living with
OL,7,Fsymptoms of coronavirus five years
OL,8,Fafter he first caught it says the
OL,9,Fresponse to the pandemic by the UK and
OL,10,FWelsh governments was "inadequate."
OL,12,FYanto Evans caught Covid in early
OL,13,F2020. He says it left him "bed-bound"
OL,14,Fwith symptoms such as struggling to
OL,15,Fstand and walk in the months that
OL,16,Ffollowed, speech loss, muscle spasms,
OL,17,Fhair loss, weight loss, insomnia,
OL,18,Fbrain fog and more.
