OL,3,C'I caught Covid in 2020 and still live
OL,4,Cwith the effects five years later'
OL,6,F"At the time I was 42, I was fit and
OL,7,Factive. I was training for a triathlon
OL,8,Fat the time," Yanto told ITV Cymru
OL,9,FWales.
OL,11,F"Even now, five years on, I'm still
OL,12,Fhaving symptoms."
OL,14,FIt comes as the UK Covid-19 inquiry
OL,15,Fwill publish a second report,
OL,16,Ffocussing on key political decisions
OL,17,Fmade in Cardiff, as well as by
OL,18,Fgovernments in London, Edinburgh, and
OL,19,FBelfast.
