OL,3,C'I caught Covid in 2020 and still live
OL,4,Cwith the effects five years later'
OL,6,F"I think today will show that the
OL,7,Fresponse to the pandemic, both by the
OL,8,FUK government and Welsh government,
OL,9,Fwas simply inadequate, pure and
OL,10,Fsimple," Yanto said.
OL,12,F"The onus right now, I think, is to
OL,13,Flearn from the latest pandemic so that
OL,14,Fwhen the next pandemic inevitably
OL,15,Farrives, we're better prepared for
OL,16,Fthat one based on what's happening
OL,17,Fright now."
