OL,3,C'I caught Covid in 2020 and still live
OL,4,Cwith the effects five years later'
OL,6,FThe inquiry, which was chaired by
OL,7,Fformer High Court judge Heather
OL,8,FHallett, held three weeks of hearings
OL,9,Fin Cardiff, with 31 witnesses from
OL,10,FWales appearing.
OL,12,FHowever, campaigners representing
OL,13,Fbereaved families remain are calling
OL,14,Ffor a separate Welsh-specific inquiry
OL,15,Fto look in more detail at the response
OL,16,Fin Wales.
OL,18,FYanto is now a trustee for the Long
OL,19,FCovid support charity, which campaigns
OL,20,Fin the UK for Long Covid to be
OL,21,Frecognised.
