OL,6,FWhat is Long Covid?
OL,8,FAccording to the NHS, Long Covid
OL,9,Fhappens when coronavirus symptoms last
OL,10,Flonger than 12 weeks.
OL,12,F"It's a new condition that's still
OL,13,Fbeing studied, but treatment can
OL,14,Fhelp," the NHS says.
